passives.name:
Rengar upgrades Bonetooth Necklace by scoring a takedown on Kha'Zix during The Hunt is On!, gaining all combined bonuses from 20 trophies as well as increased sight range while in brush.
 3 Trophies
passives.effects:
Rengar gains 25 bonus movement speed while out of combat or in brush.
 6 Trophies: Unseen Predator gains 125 bonus range.
 12 Trophies: Thrill of the Hunt's duration is increased by 5 seconds.
 20 Trophies: Thrill of the Hunt's bonus movement speed while stealthed is doubled.
